{"tid":1376750,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［車撚入］如果我架車俾人搶衝左去撞警察防線，有冇得賠？","createTime":"2019-07-28T12:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:11:52.000Z","uid":20948,"like":152,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5e3642f2415aae94276ac26681fc099bf4812899","tid":1376750,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:01:50.000Z","msg":"如果我揸車路過示威區，條路塞住左，我落車食口煙，點知俾班暴徒上左車，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">擺低塊磚頭落油門度，</span></span><br />\n駕車一嘢衝左入警察防線<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">撞飛一堆警察</span></span>，我會唔會有事上身㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然㗎車都唔係咩貴嘢，但都有買車險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw，如果巴士司機被搶巴士，架巴士又衝擊左防線，咁又司機正路都冇事㗎可<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41aa84708c6450d0505e40f4fe43442b069b33dd","tid":1376750,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"屌開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d6a2562251308b627e878ef6e37cb91bdc6a28","tid":1376750,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"線上等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86239637cedd5ab599f3e5f844188c16524dbe6a","tid":1376750,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:05:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42fb5d881bd287b3bdace278915ca10ff4678018","tid":1376750,"uid":229754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:06:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3036fbf40633d7696f604cdc856689d22fbc62f","tid":1376750,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T12:06:19.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠危險駕駛？"},{"pid":"72d1dcd99b709a22d1e48f3a58a2a99213523f58","tid":1376750,"uid":282490,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"cited